      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with regression test suite covering hemolysis transport equations; formal SQA plan documented.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and regression tests exist for Navier-Stokes components, but hemolysis scalar transport module lacks dedicated regression coverage. SQA plan is informal. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
