    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed; achieved levels below required levels in all seven cases. Six factors flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed on partial input space. Despite gaps, assessment team accepted the package for submission pending supplemental validation data commitment. Provenance chain traces from claim through validation results to experimental datasets.",
